---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Services - Coastline Spray Foam Solutions">
  <main class="container mx-auto py-20 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our Services</h1>

    <!-- Residential Insulation -->
    <section id="residential" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Residential Insulation</h2>
      <div class="md:flex md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <p class="mb-4">Coastline Spray Foam Solutions provides top-tier residential insulation services designed to make your home more energy-efficient and comfortable. Our spray foam insulation creates a powerful air barrier, sealing all the nooks and crannies where air can escape or enter. This leads to significant savings on your heating and cooling bills and a more consistent indoor temperature.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Benefits:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Lower energy consumption and utility bills.</li>
            <li>Improved indoor air quality by reducing allergens and pollutants.</li>
            <li>Enhanced soundproofing for a quieter home.</li>
            <li>Increased structural integrity of your walls.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Residential Insulation" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Commercial Insulation -->
    <section id="commercial" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Commercial Insulation</h2>
      <div class="md:flex md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <p class="mb-4">For our commercial clients, we offer robust insulation solutions that cater to the unique demands of commercial buildings. Whether it's an office, retail space, or warehouse, our spray foam insulation helps maintain a stable climate, reduce overhead costs, and create a more comfortable environment for employees and customers. We work around your schedule to minimize disruption to your business operations.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Benefits:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Substantial reduction in energy expenses.</li>
            <li>Improved employee comfort and productivity.</li>
            <li>Moisture barrier to prevent mold and mildew.</li>
            <li>Long-lasting and low-maintenance insulation solution.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Commercial Insulation" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Attic Insulation & Air Sealing -->
    <section id="attic" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Attic Insulation & Air Sealing</h2>
      <div class="md:flex md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <p class="mb-4">The attic is one of the most significant sources of energy loss in a building. Our attic insulation and air sealing services are designed to stop this loss in its tracks. We meticulously seal all air leaks and apply a thick, continuous layer of spray foam insulation to the attic floor or roofline, effectively isolating your living space from the extreme temperatures of the outdoors.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Benefits:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Prevents heat loss in the winter and heat gain in the summer.</li>
            <li>Reduces the workload on your HVAC system, extending its life.</li>
            <li>Helps prevent ice dams in colder climates.</li>
            <li>Creates a more usable and temperature-controlled attic space.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Attic Insulation" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Crawl Space Encapsulation -->
    <section id="crawl-space" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Crawl Space Encapsulation & Sealing</h2>
      <div class="md:flex md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <p class="mb-4">A damp, uninsulated crawl space can be a source of moisture, mold, and pests, affecting the entire house. Our crawl space encapsulation service involves sealing the area with a heavy-duty moisture barrier and insulating the walls with spray foam. This process transforms a problematic crawl space into a clean, dry, and conditioned part of your home, improving overall air quality and energy efficiency.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Benefits:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Eliminates moisture and reduces risk of mold and mildew.</li>
            <li>Improves indoor air quality.</li>
            <li>Makes floors warmer in the winter.</li>
            <li>Deters pests and rodents.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Crawl Space Encapsulation" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comprehensive Energy Audits -->
    <section id="energy-audit">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Comprehensive Energy Audits</h2>
      <div class="md:flex md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <p class="mb-4">Not sure where to start? Our comprehensive energy audits are the perfect first step. We use advanced diagnostic tools, such as blower doors and infrared cameras, to identify the exact areas of energy loss in your home or business. Based on our findings, we provide a detailed report and a prioritized list of recommendations to help you make the most cost-effective improvements.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Benefits:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Pinpoint sources of energy waste.</li>
            <li>Receive a customized action plan for energy savings.</li>
            <li>Make informed decisions about your insulation investment.</li>
            <li>Maximize your ROI with targeted improvements.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Energy Audit" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
